---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AmicBridge – Connect with Trusted Investors and Borrowers">
  <section class="text-center py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-blue-950 to-blue-900 text-white">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">Connecting People with Opportunity</h1>
    <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10">
      AmicBridge is a private network where verified members connect directly to trusted lenders, borrowers, and investors. 
      We don’t lend or handle money — we build bridges between people who do.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-slate-800 inline-block px-10 py-6 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2 text-blue-400">Membership Access Fee</h2>
      <p class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">$100 (one-time)</p>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
        Gain instant access to our private contact network — verified, safe, and ready for collaboration.
      </p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/4791234567" target="_blank" 
         class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition">
         💬 Message Us on WhatsApp to Join
      </a>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-sm">
        After payment verification, you’ll receive your private access link.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What You Get</h2>
    <ul class="text-gray-300 space-y-4 text-lg">
      <li>🤝 Direct introductions to verified lenders and borrowers</li>
      <li>🔐 A secure and private environment for money partnerships</li>
      <li>📈 Exclusive access to people ready to make deals now</li>
      <li>🧠 Guidance from AmicBridge to help both sides connect safely</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="text-center py-16 bg-slate-800">
    <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white mb-4">Simple, Safe, and Private</h3>
    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Once you’re inside the AmicBridge Network, you’ll receive direct contacts with people ready to lend, borrow, or invest — no banks, no waiting.
    </p>
    <a href="https://wa.me/4791234567" target="_blank" 
       class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-lg text-lg font-semibold transition">
       💬 Join the Network
    </a>
  </section>
</Layout>
